snippet.title: Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Episode 1 | 06 January 25 | Mannat's special day
snippet.description:
📲 Download JioCinema: https://bit.ly/3Be09Z3

Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Episode 1 | 06 January 25

Sonia abandons her newborn, but Shruti rescues the baby girl from the seashore and names her Mannat. Twenty-three years later, Mannat dreams of becoming the world's best chef. Will her journey lead her to uncover the truth about her past?

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannat’s biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shruti’s life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannat’s rising career, Shruti’s failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings. snippet.description:
Article 51A(h) in The Constitution Of India 
It shall be the duty of every citizen of India to develop the scientific temper, humanism and the spirit of inquiry and reform.

അത്ഭുത സിദ്ധി, അമാനുഷികത എന്ന പേരിൽ സോഷ്യൽ മീഡിയ വഴി പ്രചരിക്കുന്ന  വീഡിയോകളുടെ രഹസ്യം, റീ ക്രിയേറ്റ് ചെയ്തു കാണിക്കാനോ, മറ്റേതെങ്കിലും വീഡിയോ, ഫയലുകൾ, ഉപയോഗിച്ച് അതിൻറെ രഹസ്യം തെളിയിക്കാനോ സാധിക്കുന്നത് മാത്രമേ  എപ്പിസോഡുകളിൽ ഉൾപ്പെടുത്തുകയുള്ളൂ

പുതിയ വിഡിയോ പെട്ടെന്ന് നിങ്ങളിലേക്കെത്താൻ വിഡിയോക്ക് താഴെയുള്ള SUBSCRIBE ബട്ടൻ ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്ത ശേഷം ബെൽ ബട്ടൺ 🔔  ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്യുക

snippet.title: दिल्ली में सीएजी की रिपोर्ट, क्या राजनीति के लिए लीक की गई है?
snippet.description: क्या यह संयोग है या प्रयोग है कि दिल्ली में मुख्यमंत्री आवास को लेकर सीएजी की रिपोर्ट लीक कर दी गई? क्या इसके पहले सीएजी ने किसी और मुख्यमंत्री के सरकारी आवास के खर्चे को लेकर ऑडिट की गई है? आखिर तुलना करने का पैमाना क्या होना चाहिए? हरियाणा से लेकर मध्य प्रदेश के बीजेपी के मुख्यमंत्रियों के घर में किस किस्म के पर्दे लगे हैं, बाथरुम में क्या लगा है, हम नहीं जानते। यह सवार नैतिकता का है या भ्रष्टाचार का? देखिेए हमारा पूरा वीडियो। आख़िर तक देखिएगा।

snippet.title: Paatal Lok Season 2 - Official Trailer | Jaideep Ahlawat, Ishwak Singh, Tillotama Shome, Gul Panag
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Paatal Lok Season 2 Official Trailer
Starring Jaideep Ahlawat, Ishwak Singh, Tillotama Shome, Gul Panag, Nagesh Kukunoor, Jahnu Barua, Anurag Arora, Prashant Tamang, Merenla Imsong, LC Sekhose
Produced by Karnesh Ssharma, Babita Ashiwal
Written by Sudip Sharma, Abhishek Banerjee, Rahul Kanojia, Tamal Sen
Created by Sudip Sharma
Directed by Avinsh Arun Dhaware
A Clean Slate Filmz Production In Association With Eunoia Films

Official Release Date Jan 17, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Inspector Hathi Ram Chaudhary, the haggard, unlikely hero, investigates a high-profile murder case that leads him to remote corners of North-East India, where he battles powerful forces and personal tragedies in his pursuit of truth.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: Why are Europeans becoming POOR But HAPPIER
snippet.description:
Checkout Odoo's Accounting app - https://www.odoo.com/r/4OD 

Research reference links -  https://docs.google.com/document/d/12BDDln4ZBLz39lB0Ex5GOy_rf2_bLUmT7FPchWfFOuI/edit?usp=drivesdk 

Follow me on X → https://x.com/gauravzthakur  
Follow me on Instagram → https://instagram.com/gauravzthakur  

This paradox will blow your mind: Europeans are earning less than Americans – an average European’s income is nearly half that of an American ($44,368 vs. $81,695). Yet, Europeans rank higher on the Happiness Index, Life Expectancy, and Human Development Index.
Here’s the kicker: even unemployed Europeans are almost as happy as employed Americans! Meanwhile, Americans, despite earning double, report lower happiness levels.
How is this possible? Is happiness truly linked to money, or are Europeans living proof that less can be more? Lets understand in depth, why Europe’s economy has fallen while it's happiness has soared. This is a mystery that could redefine what we currently value the most.

Follow me on Instagram → https://instagram.com/gauravzthakur  

This paradox will blow your mind: Europeans are earning less than Americans – an average European’s income is nearly half that of an American ($44,368 vs. $81,695). Yet, Europeans rank higher on the Happiness Index, Life Expectancy, and Human Development Index.
Here’s the kicker: even unemployed Europeans are almost as happy as employed Americans! Meanwhile, Americans, despite earning double, report lower happiness levels.
How is this possible? Is happiness truly linked to money, or are Europeans living proof that less can be more? Lets understand in depth, why Europe’s economy has fallen while it's happiness has soared. This is a mystery that could redefine what we currently value the most.

snippet.title: CLASS | Zakir khan | Stand up Comedy | Sukha Puri 8
snippet.description:
Watch Zakir Khan Live In your city Tickets: https://zakirkhanlive.in 

INSTAGRAM : - https://www.instagram.com/zakirkhan_208?igsh=MTBtNzVvNW1xOTYyag==
.
.

Get ready to laugh out loud with Zakir Khan in this stand-up comedy video where he dives into the rollercoaster ride of relationships! Zakir takes on the role of a funny relationship coach, sharing his hilarious tips and relatable stories about love's ups and downs. With his unique style of mixing humor with real-life advice, he makes understanding relationships a fun experience. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy as Zakir Khan shows us how to navigate the crazy world of love while keeping it lighthearted and entertaining!

snippet.title: Carrier காலி ! Madha Gaja Raja Team Interaction | Vishal Speech at Madha Gaja Raja Pre Release Event
snippet.description:
Madha Gaja Raja is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language action comedy film directed by Sundar C and produced by Gemini Film Circuit. It stars Vishal, Anjali and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in the leading roles, while Santhanam and Sonu Sood play other pivotal supporting roles. The film began production in 2012 and was completed by 2013, but remained unreleased for over a decade due to financial troubles. It is scheduled to release in theatres on 12 January 2025, during the Pongal weekend. Madha Gaja Raja pre release event happened in chennai today. Madha Gaja Raja public review will be out on Madha Gaja Raja FDFS. Presenting Vishal, Sundar C, Vijay Antony Interview about Madha Gaja Raja movie experience. Vishal speech about Madha Gaja Raja movie experience in Madha Gaja Raja pre release event.

snippet.title: Bachelors VS Society ⚖️ - A Courtroom Drama | Baat Ka Batangad - E04 | Take A Break
snippet.description:
What happens when an entire housing society bands together against a group of carefree bachelors? Chaos, laughter, and a courtroom drama like no other! In Bachelors Vs Society, watch as tensions reach a boiling point when the society passes a new rule banning bachelors from the building. 🏢⚖️
Thrown out with all their belongings, the bachelors demand justice and call for a “society court” to prove that they’ve been unfairly targeted. What follows is a hilarious showdown where the bachelors present their side, exposing the society’s biases and poking fun at the stereotypes that surround them.
#BachelorsVsSociety #ComedySketch #CourtroomComedy

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Producer - Pratik Thakur
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

Script Supervisor - Mohd. Zaid

Associate Director - Sharjeel Shoeb

Production Manager - Pavan Tekale

snippet.title: 90's का सबसे भयानक सीन | Ashutosh Rana's Epic Scream Horror Scene | Sangharsh Movie | Preity G Zinta
snippet.description:
Lajja Shankar is attacked by all of them together, yet he manages to escape from their grasp and runs away | Sangharsh Movie Scenes

With children disappearing, mysteriously, CBI trainee, Reet Oberoi, is assigned to the case. Reet discovers that the missing children are being offered as sacrifices by Lajja Shankar Pandey (Ashutosh Rana), a religious fanatic. Unable to deal with Pandey herself, Reet gets Aman Varma to help her. However things aren't all that smooth for Aman. Will Reet and Aman subdue the evil fanatic, Pandey?

Directed by: Tanuja Chandra,  
Writing Credits: Mahesh Bhatt, Girish Dhamija, Thomas Harris,  
Cast: Preity G Zinta, Akshay Kumar, Ashutosh Rana, Vishwajeet Pradhan, Aman Verma, Madan Jain, Alia Bhatt, Ninad Kamat, Abhay Chopra, S.M. Zaheer, Arif Zakaria, Yash Tonk, Brij Bhushan Sahni, Saurabh Dubey, Rajesh Prasher, Krishna Bhatt, Sanjeeva Vatsa, Dinesh Chaturvedi, Shahad Chavan, Naushaad Abbas, Amardeep Jha, Master Mazhar, Jash Trivedi,

snippet.description:
திமுக பிரபலம் ஞானசேகரன் ஆட்டையைப் போட்ட கோவில் நிலம் 

#annauniversity #gnansekaran #dmk 

G-squareக்கும் சபரீசனுக்கும் உள்ள தொடர்பு | 30000 கோடி எங்கே இருக்கிறது ? | Saattai Exclusive - https://youtu.be/r2an_KSZOVg

விஜயகாந்த்தை வீழ்த்திய அரசியல் | எப்படி இருந்த மனுசன் ? | கண்ணீர் விடும் கட்சி தொண்டர்கள் - https://youtu.be/NTVmFpddzUI

ஜெகத்ரட்சகன் சொத்துக்களை பார்த்து மிரண்ட அதிகாரிகள் | தோண்ட தோண்ட பணக்குவியல் | கவலையில் ஸ்டாலின் - https://youtu.be/bWdzgdPP2KA

திமுகவை விரட்டி அடிக்கும் மக்கள் | உதயநிதிக்கு செருப்படி கேள்விகள் | ஸ்டாலினை திணறவைத்த பெண் - https://youtu.be/NvfpMauPjrA

Lakshmi पहुंची बुरी हालत मे Court
-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu releases its third episode of Deeksha Series. In this new episode Mahesh woke up late while every swamy is getting ready for the day, both mall and mahesh gets ready and reaches to the college. snippet.title: হুলো বিড়াল হুল্লোড় | Gopal Bhar | Episode - 1115
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

Maharaj gets upset at Maharani's cat and orders to get rid of him. How will Maharani react?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language: Bengali
Episode No: 1115

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Click to watch all the episodes of Gopal Bhar -
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASj1d8U8PvhnbuO58CfvdkLU

snippet.title: Govinda's Untold Stories Revealed: Sunita Ahuja On Her Love Story, Controversies | Raveena | Podcast
snippet.description:
Hindi Podcast: Govinda's Untold Stories Revealed: Sunita Ahuja On Her Love Story, Controversies , Raveena & more.

Dive into the fascinating life of Govinda and Sunita Ahuja as Sunita shares untold stories about their love life, Bollywood drama, family relationships, and controversies. From behind-the-scenes insights to personal revelations, this podcast is a treasure trove for Govinda fans and Bollywood enthusiasts.
